  <h2 id="seasonal-suggestions">Seasonal Suggestions</h2>
  <p>
    Take advantage of seasonal opportunities with intelligent recommendations:
  </p>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Seasonal Produce</strong>: Suggestions for fresh, in-season fruits and vegetables</li>
    <li><strong>Holiday Planning</strong>: Special lists and suggestions for holidays and events</li>
    <li><strong>Weather-Based Recommendations</strong>: Comfort foods for cold weather, fresh items for summer</li>
    <li><strong>Back-to-School</strong>: Lunch planning and school supply reminders</li>
    <li><strong>Garden Planning</strong>: Suggestions for home gardeners based on planting seasons</li>
  </ul>

  <InfoBox type="info" title="Seasonal Intelligence">
    The Planning Assistant considers over 200 seasonal factors including local weather patterns, regional holidays, and agricultural seasons to provide relevant suggestions.
  </InfoBox>

  <h2 id="inventory-management">Inventory Management</h2>
  <p>
    Keep track of what you have and what you need with smart inventory features:
  </p>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Pantry Tracking</strong>: Monitor your pantry inventory and expiration dates</li>
    <li><strong>Auto-Reorder</strong>: Automatically add items to your list when running low</li>
    <li><strong>Waste Reduction</strong>: Suggestions to use items before they expire</li>
    <li><strong>Storage Optimization</strong>: Tips for proper food storage to extend freshness</li>
    <li><strong>Inventory Alerts</strong>: Notifications about items nearing expiration</li>
  </ul>

  <div class="my-6 border border-neutral-200 dark:border-neutral-800 rounded-lg overflow-hidden">
