      Smart inventory management helps reduce food waste and ensures you never run out of essentials.
    </div>
  </div>

  <h2 id="smart-reminders">Smart Reminders</h2>
  <p>
    Never forget important shopping tasks with intelligent reminder system:
  </p>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Location-Based Reminders</strong>: Get notified when you're near stores with items on your list</li>
    <li><strong>Time-Based Alerts</strong>: Reminders based on your typical shopping schedule</li>
    <li><strong>Event Reminders</strong>: Shopping alerts before parties, holidays, or special occasions</li>
    <li><strong>Restock Notifications</strong>: Alerts when frequently used items need replenishing</li>
    <li><strong>Deal Expiration Warnings</strong>: Notifications before sales and coupons expire</li>
  </ul>

  <h2 id="customization">Customizing Your Assistant</h2>
  <p>
    Tailor the Planning Assistant to your specific needs and preferences:
  </p>
  <ul>
    <li>
      <strong>Dietary Preferences</strong>: Set vegetarian, vegan, keto, or other dietary restrictions
    </li>
    <li>
      <strong>Household Information</strong>: Number of people, ages, and special needs
    </li>
    <li>
      <strong>Budget Constraints</strong>: Set spending limits and savings goals
    </li>
    <li>
      <strong>Shopping Frequency</strong>: Customize recommendations based on how often you shop
    </li>
    <li>
      <strong>Preferred Stores</strong>: Focus suggestions on your favorite shopping locations
    </li>
    <li>
      <strong>Cooking Skill Level</strong>: Adjust recipe complexity to match your abilities
